{
  "title": "Xtra Fluffy Egyptian Rice Pilaf",
  "description": "A peppery and fluffy Egyptian dish featuring Carnaroli rice, Ssam wrap, and gluten-free friendly ingredients, this pilaf is a nostalgic treat for the senses. It is a perfect side dish for any meal.",
  "cuisine": "Egyptian",
  "diet": [
